    dc:description "Figure 17. Uvariodendron dzomboense Dagallier, Q. Luke & Couvreur A leaf, upper side B petiole and base of leaf, upper side C flower bud showing bracts, side view D flower, two outer petals and three outer petals removed E fruit with young monocarps. A-C Luke 7443 D, E Robertson MDE 207. Photos Leo-Paul Dagallier." ;
